com.bergerkiller.bukkit.tc.utils

Class TrackMovingPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bergerkiller.bukkit.tc.utils.TrackMovingPoint

  • public class TrackMovingPoint
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a Minecart moving from Block to Block. The current Minecart Block position and track position is maintained.

      • clearNext

        public void clearNext()
        Clears the next track information. After calling this method, hasNext() will return False and next() will no longer succeed.

      • next

        public void next()
        Loads in the next track information. If no next information is available, this method throws an exception. Use hasNext() to check whether next track information is available.

      • next

        public void next(boolean allowNext)
        Loads in the next track information. If no next information is available, this method throws an exception. Use hasNext() to check whether next track information is available.
        Parameters:
        allowNext - - True to allow future next() calls, False to make this one the last
